comments: Mrs. Young was my favorite professor in my time at SPC. Her classes are always interesting, and filled with a lot of interaction. Her tests can be incredibly difficult, but they really stretch you to think in a way not many other professors I\'ve had do. The group work is a pain, but it\'s a necessary evil. Reading ahead is advised, but not required.
